        "text": "皇帝",
        "label": "TITLE"
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_010_032_000017",
    "sentence": "有鵝之處舉旗，探騎馳報，遠泊鳴鼓。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_010_032_000018",
    "sentence": "鵝驚騰起，左右圍騎皆舉幟麾之。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "幟麾",
        "label": "TITLE"
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_010_032_000019",
    "sentence": "五坊擎進海東青鶻，拜授皇帝放之。",
