  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_010_032_000020",
    "sentence": "鶻擒鵝墜，勢力不加，排立近者，舉錐刺鵝，取腦以飼鶻。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_010_032_000021",
    "sentence": "救鶻人例賞銀絹。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_010_032_000022",
    "sentence": "皇帝得頭鵝，薦廟，群臣各獻酒果，舉樂。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "皇帝",
        "label": "TITLE"
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_010_032_000023",
    "sentence": "更相酬酢，致賀語，皆插鵝毛於首以為樂。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_010_032_000024",
    "sentence": "賜從人酒，遍散其毛。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_010_032_000025",
    "sentence": "弋獵網釣，春盡乃還。",
    "entities": []
  },
